{"tid":1699034,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"當李卓人輸了...","createTime":"2019-11-08T02:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T02:09:25.000Z","uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"788782a4a95aa38f321cdb2b815085dfd435dfe8","tid":1699034,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:09:25.000Z","msg":"一旦李卓人輸了，橫空下微如塵的香港，既有制度肯定進一步崩塌：議會失守、惡法重臨，特區政府與建制派，更加橫行。望着代表民主派出戰的李卓人，你我他／她腦裏或者有十萬個為什麼？但在問號之間，還是有得揀：赤色香江抑或國際香港？怕變馬凱，怕倒萬億落海，怕見林鄭月娥自鳴得意的囂張，更怕肉隨砧板上被中共任意宰割。欣●為怕，所以，更加要投票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁家傑：「如果李卓人輸咗，香港獨立關稅區一定不保，外國更加話香港係中國嘅馬仔、白手套，所以一定要出嚟投票。」周智堅攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181125/small/1543109418_6e8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181125%2Fsmall%2F1543109418_6e8a.jpg&h=d7f90797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181125/58955052\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181125%2F58955052&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUm5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=c307e0dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181125%2F58955052&h=ec66e7df\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181125/58955052</a><br />\n一個九西補選輸都會咁大後果<br />\n大家1124一定要投票呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}